"basic settings
set number "shows line number
set showcmd "shows currently typed command
colorscheme monokai "setting color scheme
syntax enable "enable syntax processing
set tabstop=4 "number of visual spaces per tab
set softtabstop=4 "number of spaces in tabs while editing
set expandtab "tabs are spaces
set cursorline "highlights current line
set wildmenu "adds a graphical menu in commands
set lazyredraw "doesn't redraw the screen during some stuff
set showmatch "shows the matching of parenthasis when cursor is on it
set incsearch "highlights search as you type
set autoindent "sets next line as same indentation as previous
set clipboard=unnamedplus "sets the clipboard to enable yanking and pasting from outside vim
set laststatus=2 "keeps the status powerline active
set colorcolumn=120 "inserts a line at 120 chars
set nowrap "removes line wrapping
set mouse=c "sets mouse to command mode
set smartcase "allows for uppercase search if exists
set ignorecase "ignores casing if lowercase search


" Window Navigation
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W><C-L>
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><C-H>

